title: The Draymond Green Show - Celtics/Nets Sweep, Warriors Lose One To Denver, and a Mailbag
itunes:title: The Draymond Green Show - Celtics/Nets Sweep, Warriors Lose One To Denver, and a Mailbag
description:
On episode 24 of 'The Draymond Green Show' Dray breaks down how the Celtics/Nets series concluded, what he thinks the Warriors need to do better against the Nuggets in game five, why Ja Morant is great but doesn't deserve Most Improved Player, and answers a few mailbag questions. #Herd

Produced by: Jackson Safon

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
